@startuml
title Label Generation Flow (With Variables)

actor User
participant "UI: Dashboard" as Dashboard
participant "API / Generator" as Generator
participant "Database" as DB

User -> Dashboard: Select Saved Label Template
Dashboard -> DB: Fetch Template Details & Variables
DB --> Dashboard: Template (with Text, Barcode, QR Variables)

Dashboard -> User: Prompt for Variable Inputs
User -> Dashboard: Enter Text Values for Variables

User -> Dashboard: Click "Generate Label"
Dashboard -> Generator: Send Template + Variable Values

== Generation Process ==
Generator -> Generator: Inject Values into Text Variables
Generator -> Generator: Convert Text to Barcode Image (Validate Constraints)
Generator -> Generator: Convert Text to QR Code Image
Generator -> Generator: Composite Elements onto Label Canvas

Generator --> Dashboard: Return Final Label Image
Dashboard -> User: Display / Download Label Image
@enduml
